### TaskManager API - Manual Testing
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or with curl/httpie
### Base URL: http://localhost:5215

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5215

### Test 1: Create a valid task with all fields
# Expected: 201 Created with Location header and complete task details
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Complete Lab 2 Manual Testing",
  "description": "Test the POST /tasks endpoint with various scenarios",
  "priority": "High",
  "dueDate": "2025-10-25T17:00:00Z"
}

### Test 2: Create a task with only required fields (no description or due date)
# Expected: 201 Created with optional fields null/empty
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Simple Task",
  "priority": "Low"
}

